  "title": "NDT Inspector (RT and PT)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Perfrom X-Ray / FPI Inspection on aircraft engine components.</li><li>Interpret work instructions and to make decisions on acceptance / rejection of parts.</li><li>Work on written instructions , operations sheets, SOP , engineering drawings and quality proceedures using X-Ray / FPI NDT Methods on aircraft enfine components to locate discontinuities.</li><li>Set up and calibrate non-destructive testing equiptments and perform daily system check.</li><li>Use NDT inspection methods to ensure maximum quality of products, defects and review test orders to determine type of test required, test procedures and part acceptability criterial.</li><li>Participate in CIP projects, audit preparations and process reports for corrective actions.</li><li>Comply with all company safety rules and regulations.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Min \"O\" Levels or equal</li><li>Willing to be based in Singapore</li><li>Strong hands on RT experience is a must</li><li>Experience level requirments: NAS 410/ EN 4179 or relevant Certification in X-Ray (RT/ FPI/ MT/ PT)</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65<strong>) </strong><a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a><strong></strong><a href=\"tel:+(65) 6514 9838\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6514 9838 </strong></a>for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
